      "content": "i tried to make some tea earlier. i just stared at the kettle waiting for it to boil and then i realized... i didn't even want it. i don't want anything. i'm just going through the motions of a life that doesn't belong to me anymore. it feels so heavy, just staying present in a world he isn't in.",
